#ThisDayinHistory 1975 Moses Kotane receives Isithwalandwe/Seaparankoe.
Moses Kotane was born in 1905 on this day, General Secretary of the SACP & ANC leader received this highest award from the ANC in 1975, 3 years before his passing in 1978. He would have turned 115 years today https://t.co/cFIUxl89ob